description: Allows you to confirm that the attached file has been uploaded using the pre-signed URL provided in the StartAttachedFileUpload API.

parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the Amazon Connect instance.

parameters.name: FileId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the attached file resource.

parameters.name: AssociatedResourceArn
parameters.description: The resource to which the attached file is (being) uploaded to. The supported resources are Cases and Email.
